Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think it is a good thing. First, it is safer for freshmen who are quite inexperienced in life to stay on campus during their first year. second, making friends is much easier when you live in a dorm and meet people constantly. Third, it gives the worried parents ease of mind.